<br>
Yes, but so far we have been able to punch while using weaps without an MA req.  Has something changed, making weaps without an MA req unable to use while punching?  If not, then I know a whole slew of weapons that are tons more powerful than the new MA weapons.  The only advantage MA skill weapons would give is that you don't have to use IP on other weapon skills as much, since a percentage of damage is based on our already high MA skill and not a new weapons skill.  From what Kicky said, though (used 2HB and a hammer) we don't reall have any IP troubles at higher level anyway, even when using IP on other weapon skills.<br>
<br>
In other words, if you use a quality 20 Sledge at level 80, you will be doing more damage than someone using a quality 20 MA weap at level 80.<br>
