<br>
I don't however know if weapons QL determines damage or if attack value does. I'd guess, weapon QL determines the possible range of damage, and attack determines the modifyers on the &quot;dice rolls.&quot; So that being the case, MA weapons would hit harder within their range of possible damage. (read as: capped at minimum against anything yellow or higher) <br>
<br>
